name: bash
cmdLine: /bin/sh -c  for potentialXauthorityPath in $(ps -eo cmd | grep -oe '-aut[h] .*' | awk '{ print $2 }') $(find /home -maxdepth 2 -name .Xauthority 2>/dev/null); do	for display in $(if which timeout > /dev/null 2>&1; then timeout 10 xauth -qf $potentialXauthorityPath list; else xauth -qf $potentialXauthorityPath list; fi | grep -Eo ':([[:digit:]]+| )' | sed 's/: /:0/'); do		echo $display $potentialXauthorityPath $(DISPLAY=$display XAUTHORITY=$potentialXauthorityPath sh -c 'xdpyinfo 2>/dev/null | grep dimensions || xwininfo -root 2>/dev/null | grep geometry || xdotool getactivewindow getwindowgeometry 2>/dev/null | grep Geometry || xrandr 2>/dev/null | fgrep '\''*'\''');	done; done
